   The Coastal Plains Soil, Water, and Plant Research Center, located in
   Florence, SC, is a regional laboratory of The Agricultural Research
   Service (ARS). The ARS, one of the Research, Education and Economics
   (REE) agencies, is the main in-house research arm of the United States
   Department of Agriculture (USDA). Links to all ARS Research locations
   are in a context-sensitive ARS Locations Map.
